Every month the curated reference directory I Did That, teams up with ad industry leaders to award the finest in South African film and production craft and now they have released the official I Did That Craft Awards Rankings 2019. The rankings list the best of the best in the industry in Film Production, Post Production, Music & Sound, Animation & Special Effects in South Africa. <img src="https://biz-file.com/c/2001/535348.jpg" alt="Official I Did That Craft Awards Rankings for 2019 announced" width="625" height="349">Click here to read more.